msgid ""
"WARNING\n"
"\n"
"This game may contain flashing lights and effects,\n"
"as well as depictions of violence and strong language."
msgstr ""
"警告\n"
"\n"
"このゲームには激しい光の点滅、\n"
"および暴力描写や乱暴な言葉遣いが含まれます。"

msgid "Special Thanks"
msgstr "スペシャルサンクス"

msgid "Everyone who made a video or stream"
msgstr "動画投稿や配信をしてくださった皆様"

msgid "Everyone who completed the survey"
msgstr "アンケートに協力してくださった皆様"

msgid "Everyone who left a comment or rating"
msgstr "コメントや評価をくださった皆様"

msgid "Our families and friends"
msgstr "家族と友人の皆様"

msgid "And You!"
msgstr "そしてあなた！"

msgid ""
"Note from the devs:\n"
"We really appreciate you taking the time to play our little game! It means the world to us!\n"
"\n"
"What you have played is the prologue of Paper Lily, a larger project we are currently working on. Right now, Chapter 1 is out so we hope you'll give it a try!\n"
"\n"
"If you liked what you played, it would help us a lot if you could leave a review!\n"
"\n"
"Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""
"開発者より:\n"
"私たちのささやかなゲームをプレイして下さりありがとうございます！私たちにとっては何物にも代えがたい喜びです！\n"
"\n"
"今プレイして頂いたのは、私たちが現在取り組んでいる、より大きなプロジェクト、Paper Lilyのプロローグに当たるものです。現在、第1章(Chapter 1)が公開中ですので、そちらも遊んでみていただければ幸いです！\n"
"\n"
"楽しんでいただけたなら、レビューを残していただけるととても助かります！\n"
"\n"
"本当にありがとうございました！"

msgid "True End K1 - Curiosity Killed the Kat"
msgstr "True End K1 - 好奇心猫をも殺す"

msgid "I need:"
msgstr "材料:"

msgid "Preparations:"
msgstr "準備:"

msgid "After waiting:"
msgstr "待った後:"

msgid "3 rooms"
msgstr "部屋 3つ"

msgid "12 candles"
msgstr "ロウソク 12本"

msgid "A lighter"
msgstr "ライター"

msgid "A rune"
msgstr "ルーン"

msgid "A tuft of hair"
msgstr "髪の毛ひとふさ"

msgid "Chalk"
msgstr "チョーク"

msgid "1) Sort the desks in each classroom"
msgstr "1) 各教室の机を脇に寄せる"

msgid "2) Turn off all the lights & draw the curtains in each classroom"
msgstr "2) 電気を全て消し、各教室のカーテンを引く"

msgid "3) Draw a path going through the 3 rooms (with chalk)"
msgstr "3) 3つの部屋を貫く道を描く (チョークで)"

msgid "4) In the middle room, place one candle on each desk"
msgstr "4) 真ん中の部屋の机に1本ずつロウソクを置く"

msgid "5) Light the candles & wait at least 5 minutes"
msgstr "5) ロウソクを灯し、最低5分待つ"

msgid "6) Burn the tuft of hair on one of the candles"
msgstr "6) 髪の毛の束をロウソクのうち1つで燃やす"

msgid "7) Blow out all of the candles"
msgstr "7) ロウソクを全て吹き消す"

msgid "8) Close your eyes and count to 100"
msgstr "8) 目を閉じて100まで数える"

msgid "9) Open your eyes and then ?????????"
msgstr "9) 目を開けると…?????????"

msgid "Something like this ??"
msgstr "こんな感じ？？"

msgid "Windows (CLOSE CURTAINS!!)"
msgstr "窓 (カーテン閉める！！)"

msgid "White chalk lines"
msgstr "白いチョークの線"

msgid "Me"
msgstr "私"

msgid "Desks (candle on each)"
msgstr "机 (ロウソク置く)"

msgid "???"
msgstr "？？？"

msgid "Ponytail Girl"
msgstr "ポニーテールの少女"

msgid "Pretty Girl"
msgstr "かわいい少女"

msgid "Quiet Girl"
msgstr "物静かな少女"
